::Aerotaur::
    "TRINITY!!!"  He screams and reaches down lifting the rest of the plants 
off of the top.  The top cleared he pried his fingers under the lid and 
pulled as hard as he could.  The top was pulled free and flung a few feet.  
He drew his staff and pointed it at Nightlight's head.  "No sudden movements, 
Trinity get out of there."
